```

```ts
declare function identity<T>(x?: T): T;

const r = identity(); // no argument, no default, no constraint
//    ^? what is the type of `r`?
```

Answer with the single type name TypeScript uses here.

```ts
type Flatten<T> = T extends Array<infer Inner> ? Flatten<Inner> : T;

type R = Flatten<number[][][]>;
```

